{"tid":772804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】怕咗侵爺 傳中國延推「大灣區」計劃","createTime":"2018-08-09T05:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T06:43:08.000Z","uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a45afd5821d6b09ff0d79fe4345a8d9799cc45fd","tid":772804,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:05:13.000Z","msg":"大灣區出現變數！據《南華早報》引消息報道，中方為避免重蹈「中國製造2025」覆轍，成為美國加稅清單目標，決定將「大灣區」計劃延遲推行。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，將計劃推遲主要源於貿易戰，現時中方面對的局面是，若果將「大灣區」計劃規模縮減，又怕「冇面」；但如果計劃規模宏大，則怕刺激美國會有新戰靶。有見及此，中方將不會一次過公佈所有措施，反而會將措施逐一推出。"},{"pid":"bd3aaaf3fab7c88b424e5766f32694178687fb12","tid":772804,"uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:05:49.000Z","msg":"大灣區必定打到美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a421c34cd83f2551e7edf8ae7fdef90507d256fe","tid":772804,"uid":153778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"中國一定係最大赢家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0c772f869532c2a30e526e969b515dd4cb2615","tid":772804,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b37b4a66cca061d9d7f1294cb56e830aaa31bf8","tid":772804,"uid":33483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"支那不嬲都唔要面架啦 <br />\n學咩人講面子姐"},{"pid":"de8635adaa6d4d7d9c5519f55bc93f180d0b3014","tid":772804,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"中國唔可以縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afe3bff0851c6fd572549a624f34901ca942d81","tid":772804,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"de8635adaa6d4d7d9c5519f55bc93f180d0b3014","tid":772804,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:07:02.000Z","msg":"中國唔可以縮<img src=\"/assets/fac